{"author":{"id":"8b4e58f5679bcce787fd551e8e87fa9849dbb7627d4f14ea3898f84c8a9da805"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1448491197,"nonce":"03o+dbg0vHrW4rG/+xZkCcb10gw=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDE1OTc0NzQ2Mg==","github-url":"https://github.com/galaxyproject/tools-iuc/issues/299#issuecomment-159747462"},"message":"Hi everyone,\n\nThanks for this very interesting proposal!\n\nA litlle message to inform you that we will be ~10 people from France interested by this Hackathon. Thanks to western France GUGGO Galaxy group, INRIA, the French Institut of Bioinformatics and the Environmental Genomics CNRS group, we will centralized some actions at INRIA, Rennes.\n\nAnybody can consult our draft of program (https://cesgo.genouest.org/groups/guggo/wiki/MEtagenomicsHackathon) but briefly, we planned to work on:\n- a new INRA Metagenomics Galaxy pipeline dedicated to find OTU, named FROGS ( [poster](https://www.researchgate.net/publication/282656276_FROGS_Find_Rapidly_OTUs_with_Galaxy_Solution), [Galaxy tools](https://github.com/geraldinepascal/FROGS), [test Genocloud instance](http://cloud-55.genouest.org/galaxy/)) using [Swarm](http://www.mn.uio.no/ifi/english/research/networks/clsi/seminars/061113.html)\n- an IFREMER Metagenomics Galaxy pipeline dedicated to find OTU based on Qiime\n- an ECOBIO Metagenomics Galaxy pipeline dedicated to find OTU based on Mothur\n- the ASaiM pipeline to work on metagenomics / metatranscriptomics data ([Galaxy Day presentation](http://bebatut-slides.github.io/galaxy-day_2015/#/1/3))\n\nWe will probably focus primarily on the toolshedization / dockerization / IFB cloudification of FROGS and ASaiM. Then, if we have time and/or if people particularly interested by these tasks, we propose to work on the modification of \"home-made\" Mothur and Qiime Galaxy tools.\n\nI don't really know how a remote hackathon can work, So don't hesitate to give me some advices / informations.\n\nWe canhave opportunities for visioconfernece through [Renater Rendez-vous](https://rendez-vous.renater.fr/galhackmetafr)","files":null}]}